  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/f89999b53192cdbe6924ac3ffdfe84f7.poster.avif?t=1769708683\" width=640 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/f89999b53192cdbe6924ac3ffdfe84f7.webm?t=1769708683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/f89999b53192cdbe6924ac3ffdfe84f7.mp4?t=1769708683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A boy and an old man stand in front a pond, waiting for a swan's song. Meanwhile, they talk about life, death, and the passage of time.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💬 Dialogue-based <strong>short story</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👦👴 Themes of <i>growing up</i>, <i>life expectations</i> and <i>dealing with regret</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦢 <strong>45 minutes</strong> of waiting for the <i>swan's song</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪶 The title is <strong>not a typo</strong>! Find out why.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 Art made by hand by <strong>Federico Castillo</strong>, nominated for <strong>Best Poster</strong> at the <i>Rome Prisma Independent Film Awards 2024</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✍️ Story written by <strong>Luis León</strong>, nominated for the <strong>Digital Moment Award</strong> at <i>AMAZE Festival 2024</i> and the Opening Up category at the <i>New Media Writing Prize 2025</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 The story <strong>does not feature multiple endings</strong>, it's more of an <strong>interactive theatre</strong> experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/548e2e280ff9ebb5081df2177a4fc21f.poster.avif?t=1769708683\" width=640 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/548e2e280ff9ebb5081df2177a4fc21f.webm?t=1769708683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3598860/extras/548e2e280ff9ebb5081df2177a4fc21f.mp4?t=1769708683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
